cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.CE 

The paper involves the use of satellite imagery and artificial neural networks for modeling and predicting deforestation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of neural networks also suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The study also involves spatial analysis and information systems, which could be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE) sub-categories.
